{
  "stem": "11274.4",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a scribe there taking the names and the numbers and writing them down, at least I think so.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All of them, all 50 of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Mengele wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he had a SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "On this side is roll call.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we are on the other side, just the 50 separated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there are three or four SS counting the people here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody's counting us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We're just standing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And suddenly, somebody comes out from behind the building, Mengele's building, with a sheet of paper and a pencil.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And anybody who had a sheet of paper and a pencil, they're walking around while everybody else was roll call, was somebody, a prominent-- either a block elder or had some function more than just the plain people, like I was and Danka, working in the field outside.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I see her pointing at-- at somebody that she knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she called her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw her getting in the paper, and scratching something out-- scratching her name out, and took her away, went behind the block.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to Danka, I said, guess what?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, there were some of them that go to-- there were some rumors that Mengele is doing sterilization and all kinds of other experiments.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and she took out this one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she's a prominent person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If she knew we were happy to be in that detail because maybe finally, this is already so many months later-- and another winter is coming.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're gonna be working outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were happy we were gonna be maybe somewhere under a roof, maybe in a sewing room or somewhere, in a better-- in a better detail.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, this could not be a good detail.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
